{"tid":2040110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民進黨：台灣絕不會割席放棄香港，承諾與香港人站在一起","createTime":"2020-05-28T11:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T04:33:40.000Z","uid":52658,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7e77c82eae37ac91c9a371ed3fc7927fda437ef","tid":2040110,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:06:39.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣書店創辦人林榮基擔心，港澳條例停用恐影響人道援助和港人居留，民進黨副秘書長林飛帆今天拜會林榮基時強調「台灣不會割席」，總統蔡英文的說法不是放棄香港，而是要同國際所有民主夥伴一起，嚴正警告中國懸崖勒馬。<br />\n<br />\n對於日前蔡總統公開表達將「和香港人民站在一起」，林飛帆說，他特別向林榮基說明，就他的理解，總統所提的「依據台灣的香港澳門關係條例第60條，香港情勢一旦發生變化，可停止適用該條例一部或全部」，這個意思並非放棄香港，相反的，是要清楚的正告中國政府，如果中國片面撕毀對香港人民的承諾，台灣也會同國際社會善盡力量做出相應措施。"},{"pid":"74b0e9996c546bbc493bbedc73cf4eb28d3cccca","tid":2040110,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608600924b1b05a382be893bf28b37e8ca9485f5","tid":2040110,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a111b9dc21e1a3dee49616cd36f61a3d2ec386","tid":2040110,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baedffd85b77effa80f3d0048d1c684853aed14","tid":2040110,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}